These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | december | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, lemon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growsaconite is not the person eating lemon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | apple | lemon      |
| Pet    | aconite  | azalea |

 #################################

 
