City: marseilles, prague
1. the person watching superhero movies is not the person traveling to prague##6
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | superhero |
| Sport         | prague | marseilles      |

